org.jasig.cas.authentication.principal
类 PersonDirectoryPrincipalResolver

java.lang.Object
  org.jasig.cas.authentication.principal.PersonDirectoryPrincipalResolver
所有已实现的接口：
PrincipalResolver
public class PersonDirectoryPrincipalResolver
extends Object
implements PrincipalResolver

Resolves principals by querying a data source using the Jasig Person Directory API. The Principal.getAttributes() are populated by the results of the query and the principal ID may optionally be set by proving an attribute whose first non-null value is used; otherwise the credential ID is used for the principal ID.

从以下版本开始：
4.0
作者：
Marvin S. Addison

supports

public boolean supports(Credential credential)
从接口 PrincipalResolver 复制的描述
Determines whether this instance supports principal resolution from the given credential. This method SHOULD be called prior to PrincipalResolver.resolve(org.jasig.cas.authentication.Credential).

指定者：
接口 PrincipalResolver 中的 supports
参数：
credential - The credential to check for support.
返回：
True if credential is supported, false otherwise.

指定者：
接口 PrincipalResolver 中的 resolve
参数：

返回：

extractPrincipalId

protected String extractPrincipalId(Credential credential)
Extracts the id of the user from the provided credential. This method should be overridded by subclasses to achieve more sophisticated strategies for producing a principal ID from a credential.

参数：
credential - the credential provided by the user.
返回：
the username, or null if it could not be resolved.
